channel.title: WIMMEL Portfolio Website
channel.description: Recent content on WIMMEL Portfolio Website

item.title: GraphWar Line Generation Program
item.description: Coded a python program to generate scaled piecewise equations that go through user-inputted click positions in the game Graph War.

item.title: Small Project: KSC75 (Headphones) Detachable Cable Mod
item.description: Combined and modified various obj/stl files to quickly develop a functional mounting bracket for a female 2 pin jack. Soldered and glued the jack in for the complete functional mod.

item.title: Automatic Door Opening System
item.description: Collaborated with one of my peers to design and develop a sensor/arduino controlled automatic door system, reducing costs 90% compared to industry standards.

item.title: Small Project: Moai Keycaps
item.description: Combined and modified various obj/stl files to quickly develop functional 3D-printed moai keycaps with acceptable fitment and strength.
